tournament.name: MN Gate Fair 2025
tournament.description:
We are so excited to welcome you back to Can Can Wonderland for Minnesota Gate Fair 2024! This year's theme will be Battle of the Bands! 
Group stage on Saturday, August 23rd. Double Elimination Stage on Sunday, August 24th.
tournament.registration_message: The KQ MPLS scene is so excited to welcome you back to Can Can Wonderland for Minnesota Gate Fair 2025! A $40 registration fee will get you entrance into Can Can for the weekend, and some tourney SWAG, along with encore games at Bad Penny! Please send registration to the Venmo @Chloe-Nelson-2000! We can't wait to see you rock and roll in the land of 10,000 Lakes!

We are so excited to welcome you back to Can Can Wonderland for Minnesota Gate Fair 2024! This year's theme will be Battle of the Bands! 
Group stage on Saturday, August 23rd. Double Elimination Stage on Sunday, August 24th.
tournament.registration_message: The KQ MPLS scene is so excited to welcome you back to Can Can Wonderland for Minnesota Gate Fair 2025! A $40 registration fee will get you entrance into Can Can for the weekend, and some tourney SWAG, along with encore games at Bad Penny! Please send registration to the Venmo @Chloe-Nelson-2000! We can't wait to see you rock and roll in the land of 10,000 Lakes!
